<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Qapture</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Capture Moments, Share Joy</h1>
            <p>Your Digital Memory Box for Every Event</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="introduction">
        <div class="container">
            <p>Welcome to Qapture, the digital memory box that revolutionizes how you capture, share, and relive your most cherished moments. Whether it’s a wedding, birthday, or corporate event, Qapture ensures that every memory is preserved and shared effortlessly.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="feature">
                <h2>Seamless Photo Sharing</h2>
                <p>Effortlessly upload and share photos from your event with all attendees.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2>Video Messages</h2>
                <p>Collect heartfelt video messages from your guests, adding a personal touch to your memory box.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2>Digital Memory Box</h2>
                <p>Create a lasting digital keepsake that holds all your event’s memories in one place.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2>Easy Access</h2>
                <p>Access your memories anytime, anywhere via our intuitive web app.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2>QR Code Invitations</h2>
                <p>Simplify the process of inviting guests to contribute with unique QR codes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Create an Event: Set up your event in just a few clicks.</li>
                <li>Invite Guests: Share your unique event QR code with guests to enable contributions.</li>
                <li>Capture Memories: Guests can upload photos, videos, and messages during the event.</li>
                <li>Enjoy and Share: Relive the event anytime with your beautifully organized digital memory box.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="visual-showcase">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Gallery of Images/Videos</h2>
            <div class="gallery">
                <!-- Showcase images and videos here -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div>
            <h2>Ready to capture and share your memories?</h2>
            <p>Sign up now and start your first event with Qapture!</p>
            <%= link_to 'Get Started', new_user_registration_path, class: 'button' %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Email: support@qapture.com</p>
                <div class="social-media">
                    <%= link_to image_tag('facebook-icon.png', alt: 'Facebook'), '#' %>
                    <%= link_to image_tag('instagram-icon.png', alt: 'Instagram'), '#' %>
                    <%= link_to image_tag('twitter-icon.png', alt: 'Twitter'), '#' %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="links">
                <%= link_to 'Home', root_path %>
                <%= link_to 'FAQs', faqs_path %>
                <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', privacy_policy_path %>
                <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', terms_of_service_path %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .introduction, .features, .how-it-works, .visual-showcase, .call-to-action {
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .features .feature {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .features h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .how-it-works h2, .call-to-action h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .how-it-works ol {
            list-style: decimal inside;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .visual-showcase .gallery {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .call-to-action p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .call-to-action .button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #fff;
            background: #333;
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer .contact-info {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer .social-media img {
            width: 24px;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .footer .links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
